Phandom drama? It's more likely than you think.

.

My ask box is always open if you need a place to be dramatic, share theories, conspiracies, opinions, or general grievances. Fire away, my babies. Nothing is off limits. (Except for the things that are.)

.

Icon by phanniephobic, header by cinnamonnutlester

body:
The Marshmallow Vid: a recap

-I like those hoodies on them


-Phil called me a snacc and then took it bacc


-oh so it’s a spon vid. Not my faves but alright.


-Dan’s foodsona is a single piece of black licorice and yeah that seems about right


-(my foodsona would be a big sticky bowl of Mac and cheese with ground beef if you were wondering)


-wow I wonder why phil likes bamboo rice idk it’s impossible to tell


-so milk is the one with the big titties Okay app I see you


-“thick bush” followed immediately by “nut cannon” and in other news I’ve unsubscribed from amazingphil.


-Dan hates buffets and in other news I’ve unsubscribed from danisnotonfire


-“alone at the romance table” is gonna he the title of my autobiography.


-“I wouldn’t mind sitting in a tree with a hamburger” what a mood.


-“spicy gluten” did you mean, my stripper name?


Overall: I didn’t like this video for the sole fact that it was a spon for some random game I have no interest in, but there were some interesting quotes so points for that.
